            <title>[LU-13710] llapi_file_get_stripe.3 needs to be updated for new layout types</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13710</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;llapi_file_get_stripe.3&lt;/tt&gt; man page should be updated to describe the new file layout types for PFL, DoM, and FLR, and their corresponding &lt;tt&gt;LOV_MAGIC_&amp;#42;&lt;/tt&gt; values, but also encourage users to use the &lt;tt&gt;llapi_layout_&amp;#42;.3&lt;/tt&gt; interfaces for more complex layouts, rather than trying to interpret them in userspace. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
